The instructions on this DVD were detailed and clear.  Angela Bailey is an amazing instructor.  I recommend this DVD to any professional and aspiring model, and also to the everyday woman.  Effective runway presence is about confidence.  As an aspiring model the skills I learn on this DVD helped my execute like a pro on the runway.  My mother watch the DVD with me and she was able to learn skills that helped her carry herself  with poise in the corporate board and business office.
